Alright, look at my leg.

3
00:00:03,270 --> 00:00:03,990
Open your legs

4
00:00:04,630 --> 00:00:06,350
and close your heels.

5
00:00:06,430 --> 00:00:07,580
Right! Well done!

6
00:00:07,830 --> 00:00:09,030
Well, now we learn the hands.

7
00:00:09,310 --> 00:00:09,990
Hands.

8
00:00:10,870 --> 00:00:11,870
Put them down.

9
00:00:32,259 --> 00:00:35,030
[Summer Again]

10
