[Summer Again.
Episode 18: The Seed of Jealousy]

11
00:00:38,610 --> 00:00:40,750
[Adapted from Huo He's comic, "Mint Love"]

12
00:00:52,670 --> 00:00:55,590
Oh, oops, how did the ball
grow legs and run away?

13
00:00:56,310 --> 00:00:57,550
Could you help me to pick it?

14
00:00:59,230 --> 00:01:00,350
Don't you have legs?

15
00:01:02,030 --> 00:01:02,550
No.

16
00:01:04,989 --> 00:01:05,710
Troublesome!

17
00:01:08,310 --> 00:01:09,150
Hey, your ball.

18
00:01:09,350 --> 00:01:09,910
Thank you.

19
00:01:10,710 --> 00:01:11,270
Thanks.

20
00:01:13,110 --> 00:01:14,230
Why did you two come over?

21
00:01:14,789 --> 00:01:15,190
Oh, why?

22
00:01:15,190 --> 00:01:16,789
Do we have to report you that we came?

23
00:01:16,900 --> 00:01:18,870
We just got to know from the
class group chat that,

24
00:01:19,100 --> 00:01:20,750
Wang Yi Ming has competition today.

25
00:01:20,830 --> 00:01:21,950
So, we want to cheer with him.

26
00:01:23,789 --> 00:01:26,789
You two just come to see him particularly?

27
00:01:28,950 --> 00:01:30,950
The best vanguard of basketball club.

28
00:01:31,150 --> 00:01:32,390
I won't let you disappoint!

29
00:01:35,430 --> 00:01:36,750
See! Like I said.

30
00:01:36,750 --> 00:01:38,550
Wang Yi Ming
is great in playing basketball.

31
00:01:38,630 --> 00:01:40,190
This is the first time I see him playing.

32
00:01:43,270 --> 00:01:44,030
Go for it!

33
00:01:48,070 --> 00:01:49,789
Go for it, vanguard!

34
00:01:49,870 --> 00:01:50,550
Go for it!

35
00:01:50,630 --> 00:01:51,550
Go for it!

36
00:02:02,900 --> 00:02:03,750
What are you thinking of?

37
00:02:04,550 --> 00:02:05,350
Nothing.

38
00:02:06,270 --> 00:02:07,630
I just feel little bit tired.

39
00:02:09,590 --> 00:02:11,260
I thought you are still
thinking of the ballet.

40
00:02:12,750 --> 00:02:13,710
How could it be?

41
00:02:14,780 --> 00:02:16,230
How could I think of ballet?

42
00:02:20,190 --> 00:02:20,710
Okay.

43
00:02:22,230 --> 00:02:23,790
Well, I just feel little bit strange.

44
00:02:25,030 --> 00:02:26,340
Today, when Xiao Bei asked me

45
00:02:26,590 --> 00:02:27,950
about what to teach him,

46
00:02:28,230 --> 00:02:29,829
the first thing I thought

47
00:02:30,710 --> 00:02:32,030
was ballet.

48
00:02:33,630 --> 00:02:34,990
At that time, I hesitated for some time.

49
00:02:35,550 --> 00:02:36,630
But after I thought about it,

50
00:02:36,950 --> 00:02:38,270
there is nothing

51
00:02:38,660 --> 00:02:40,470
I could really teach him except ballet.

52
00:02:42,510 --> 00:02:43,230
Well, you can teach him a lot of things.

53
00:02:43,230 --> 00:02:45,790
You can teach him singing, story telling

54
00:02:46,030 --> 00:02:47,020
or making one thousand paper cranes.//

55
00:02:47,590 --> 00:02:50,100
But all you thought of was ballet.

56
00:02:52,150 --> 00:02:53,910
You have been dancing ballet
through many years

57
00:02:54,790 --> 00:02:56,070
but do you ever feel that

58
00:02:56,270 --> 00:02:57,350
you got special feeling from ballet?

59
00:02:58,270 --> 00:02:58,750
I...

60
00:03:03,390 --> 00:03:05,550
And how do you know about
Xiao Bei's matter?

61
00:03:05,830 --> 00:03:07,550
Did that Miss Editor of yours tell you?

62
00:03:09,030 --> 00:03:09,710
No, not her.

63
00:03:10,510 --> 00:03:11,550
You met that person before.

64
00:03:11,550 --> 00:03:12,350
He is

65
00:03:13,100 --> 00:03:13,830
Wei Ze.

66
00:03:14,030 --> 00:03:15,190
Senior Wei Ze?

67
00:03:16,510 --> 00:03:17,430
No wonder.

68
00:03:17,500 --> 00:03:19,670
He even came to ask me about
your phone number.

69
00:03:20,550 --> 00:03:21,230
Wait a second!

70
00:03:21,460 --> 00:03:23,350
Senior Wei Ze knows that you are Qing He?

71
00:03:23,660 --> 00:03:25,870
Correct. He met me
on that day of the signing event.

72
00:03:26,670 --> 00:03:27,829
I see.

73
00:03:28,310 --> 00:03:30,030
I asked him how you look like.

74
00:03:30,310 --> 00:03:32,110
He told me that you look so friendly.

75
00:03:32,579 --> 00:03:33,350
Then I said,

76
00:03:33,460 --> 00:03:35,510
how could anyone describe
others as they look friendly?

77
00:03:38,740 --> 00:03:40,670
And he told me that
he admired you before.

78
00:03:41,030 --> 00:03:42,110
Would that be...

79
00:03:43,790 --> 00:03:44,510
Hey! What are you thinking of?

80
00:03:48,829 --> 00:03:50,230
Hey! When did you start
playing basketball?

81
00:03:51,310 --> 00:03:54,030
From standard five or six.

82
00:03:54,510 --> 00:03:56,870
Then you must have learned from
professional coach, right?

83
00:03:57,030 --> 00:03:58,220
Otherwise, it could not
just have been four or five years

84
00:03:58,220 --> 00:03:59,710
then you played it well!

85
00:04:00,550 --> 00:04:02,430
No! It is about the talent.

86
00:04:02,950 --> 00:04:03,990
I got something, I need to go first.

87
00:04:07,460 --> 00:04:08,030
Tao Zi!

88
00:04:09,310 --> 00:04:10,950
So, can you teach me how to play
the basketball?

89
00:04:12,300 --> 00:04:12,710
Sure.

90
00:04:13,620 --> 00:04:15,150
Let's go to eat something.

91
00:05:14,990 --> 00:05:16,780
[You have been dancing ballet
for so many years]

92
00:05:17,510 --> 00:05:18,950
[but do you ever feel that]

93
00:05:19,230 --> 00:05:20,300
[you got special feeling from ballet?]

94
00:06:06,950 --> 00:06:07,550
Tong Tong!

95
00:06:08,430 --> 00:06:09,350
Did you sleep already?

96
00:06:11,070 --> 00:06:11,990
No, not yet.

97
00:06:14,220 --> 00:06:15,390
Your dad sent something to you.

98
00:06:15,430 --> 00:06:16,950
The glutinous rice ball which he made.

99
00:06:17,110 --> 00:06:17,950
For your supper.

100
00:06:18,030 --> 00:06:18,950
From my dad?

101
00:06:20,670 --> 00:06:21,030
Try it.

102
00:06:23,190 --> 00:06:23,910
Tasty!

103
00:06:23,950 --> 00:06:24,230
Tasty?

104
00:06:24,230 --> 00:06:25,430
My dad's cooking skill got improved.

105
00:06:26,550 --> 00:06:27,830
The semester is starting soon.

106
00:06:28,030 --> 00:06:30,230
Have you made your decision?
Arts stream or Science stream?

107
00:06:32,909 --> 00:06:33,950
Maybe Arts stream.

108
00:06:34,270 --> 00:06:35,790
I think I am still better in arts.

109
00:06:35,870 --> 00:06:38,190
Arts... Arts is good too.

110
00:06:39,270 --> 00:06:40,390
You can learn whatever you want,

111
00:06:40,550 --> 00:06:41,790
as long as you like it

112
00:06:42,030 --> 00:06:43,510
and I will not stop you.

113
00:06:44,110 --> 00:06:45,070
Thank you, Mum!

114
00:06:57,670 --> 00:06:58,310
Yue Ming.

115
00:06:58,870 --> 00:06:59,590
We did not meet and
you grew even taller

116
00:06:59,630 --> 00:07:00,660
after the holiday.

117
00:07:00,710 --> 00:07:02,070
Not only growing taller,

118
00:07:02,070 --> 00:07:03,350
I gained some weight too.

119
00:07:04,390 --> 00:07:07,260
The day of staying late at night has come.

120
00:07:07,260 --> 00:07:08,190
Indeed!

121
00:07:09,670 --> 00:07:11,150
It is new semester soon.

122
00:07:11,390 --> 00:07:12,910
It's also a brand new start.

123
00:07:13,030 --> 00:07:13,670
Tong Xi.

124
00:07:16,230 --> 00:07:16,990
Oh my...

125
00:07:17,470 --> 00:07:20,190
Isn't this the best oyster cake
from that Xi Zhao Lane?

126
00:07:20,310 --> 00:07:21,510
It is very hard to buy it!

127
00:07:21,590 --> 00:07:22,550
It only opens in the morning,

128
00:07:22,670 --> 00:07:24,510
and you have to spend almost an hour
waiting at the long queue

129
00:07:24,510 --> 00:07:25,230
before you could buy it.

130
00:07:25,790 --> 00:07:28,550
Lin, you are so considerate.

131
00:07:29,230 --> 00:07:29,990
Have a taste.

132
00:07:32,750 --> 00:07:35,030
Well, maybe I recently ate too much Pocky

133
00:07:35,070 --> 00:07:36,150
and I have cloyed of it.

134
00:07:36,510 --> 00:07:38,180
Have something greasy then!
To cleanse the palate.

135
00:07:44,630 --> 00:07:46,230
It's just the first day of the school.

136
00:07:46,590 --> 00:07:47,790
Look! All of you!

137
00:07:47,870 --> 00:07:49,030
Like you never wake from sleep.

138
00:07:49,110 --> 00:07:50,750
Class streaming will start soon.

139
00:07:50,909 --> 00:07:52,470
There's a common saying.

140
00:07:52,590 --> 00:07:55,510
"Junior two and senior two
are the most important turning points."

141
00:07:56,070 --> 00:07:57,190
Get this chance!

142
00:07:57,270 --> 00:07:58,980
Study well and you will succeed

143
00:07:59,070 --> 00:08:00,190
otherwise you will fail.

144
00:08:00,590 --> 00:08:01,270
Of course.

145
00:08:01,950 --> 00:08:03,550
I hope that every student from our class

146
00:08:03,550 --> 00:08:04,430
will succeed.

147
00:08:04,510 --> 00:08:06,070
Come on, be more energetic!

148
00:08:12,510 --> 00:08:13,110
This is correct.

149
00:08:13,710 --> 00:08:15,230
This is the true attitude that

150
00:08:15,260 --> 00:08:16,630
a senior two student should have.

151
00:08:17,350 --> 00:08:17,750
By the way,

152
00:08:18,270 --> 00:08:19,230
before the class,

153
00:08:19,310 --> 00:08:20,310
I want to mention one thing.

154
00:08:20,830 --> 00:08:22,190
As you all saw the school's
notification that

155
00:08:22,750 --> 00:08:23,630
this weekend

156
00:08:23,670 --> 00:08:24,910
is our school's Community Day.

157
00:08:25,030 --> 00:08:27,150
This is also the last activity before
the class streaming.

158
00:08:27,260 --> 00:08:29,310
And the students who want to
apply for the poverty allowance

159
00:08:29,430 --> 00:08:31,430
also have to attend this activity
like previous year.

160
00:08:31,710 --> 00:08:33,190
The subsidy amount of this year

161
00:08:33,270 --> 00:08:35,230
has increased 50% compare to last year.

162
00:08:35,390 --> 00:08:36,830
And students who need to apply,

163
00:08:36,909 --> 00:08:38,830
please get the application form
from class monitor tomorrow.

164
00:08:38,909 --> 00:08:41,309
After filling it, send it to my office.
Okay?

165
00:08:43,230 --> 00:08:43,830
Would you go

166
00:08:43,950 --> 00:08:45,390
to dig the clams with us ?

167
00:08:45,470 --> 00:08:46,740
That sounds interesting!

168
00:08:46,830 --> 00:08:47,790
No, I'm not going.

169
00:08:47,870 --> 00:08:49,030
I have extra class this weekend.

170
00:08:49,230 --> 00:08:51,270
Furthermore, I don't need that allowance.

171
00:08:51,350 --> 00:08:52,430
Just let it be.

172
00:08:53,310 --> 00:08:54,070
Alright.

173
00:08:54,900 --> 00:08:59,080
[Blue Elephant]

174
00:08:56,150 --> 00:08:58,990
What is the "Community Day"
that the teacher said

175
00:08:59,060 --> 00:08:59,940
during the class today?

176
00:09:00,150 --> 00:09:01,830
How come I had never heard it before?

177
00:09:02,750 --> 00:09:04,470
It is just one of our school activities.

178
00:09:04,750 --> 00:09:06,790
In the previous year,
we paid a visit to the orphanage

179
00:09:06,790 --> 00:09:07,910
to see little kids

180
00:09:07,910 --> 00:09:08,870
and played with them.

181
00:09:08,910 --> 00:09:10,590
But this year we might go to the seaside

182
00:09:10,630 --> 00:09:12,150
and help the fishermen
for beachcombing.

183
00:09:12,150 --> 00:09:14,350
I heard that students who
applied for poverty allowance

184
00:09:14,350 --> 00:09:15,230
are obligated to participate it.

185
00:09:15,310 --> 00:09:16,780
And others simply apply as volunteers.

186
00:09:17,110 --> 00:09:18,590
We don't apply for allowance,

187
00:09:19,510 --> 00:09:20,790
then it has nothing to do with us.

188
00:09:22,150 --> 00:09:25,430
Does "beachcombing" mean,
using the small shovel

189
00:09:25,470 --> 00:09:26,900
to dig the clams at the beach?

190
00:09:27,550 --> 00:09:29,430
Although I grew up in Xi Hai,

191
00:09:29,470 --> 00:09:30,590
I'd never experienced that before.

192
00:09:30,670 --> 00:09:31,510
I really wish to try it.

193
00:09:32,180 --> 00:09:33,430
That also sounds interesting to me.

194
00:09:33,630 --> 00:09:34,550
I would like to try it

195
00:09:34,630 --> 00:09:35,590
even without the allowance.

196
00:09:35,670 --> 00:09:36,630
Let's apply it together then.

197
00:09:36,670 --> 00:09:37,110
Great!

198
00:09:37,670 --> 00:09:39,270
If you want to go,

199
00:09:39,710 --> 00:09:40,470
bring me too.

200
00:09:47,510 --> 00:09:49,460
If the three of you go,

201
00:09:49,710 --> 00:09:50,340
then I...

202
00:09:51,270 --> 00:09:53,230
I will go with you all!

203
00:09:53,830 --> 00:09:54,710
You?

204
00:09:54,950 --> 00:09:56,940
You just go accompanying
your Sun Jie Ping.

205
00:09:59,630 --> 00:10:01,340
Stop the nonsense!

206
00:10:01,510 --> 00:10:03,150
She is a girl.

207
00:10:03,230 --> 00:10:05,070
It is bad for her if you say like this.

208
00:10:05,510 --> 00:10:06,310
I don't care.

209
00:10:06,550 --> 00:10:07,500
I must go.

210
00:10:08,630 --> 00:10:09,510
And don't leave me alone!

211
00:10:10,790 --> 00:10:11,550
Fine!

212
00:10:11,630 --> 00:10:12,990
We will apply together.

213
00:10:13,270 --> 00:10:15,190
Otherwise, there won't be
any chance for the activities

214
00:10:15,230 --> 00:10:16,330
after class streaming

215
00:10:19,630 --> 00:10:20,820
When you do the multiplication,
the first one

216
00:10:21,030 --> 00:10:24,520
multiples with the first one.
The last one multiples with the last one.

217
00:10:24,670 --> 00:10:25,830
Isn't it easier?

218
00:10:26,430 --> 00:10:28,670
Sister, I don't want to do it anymore.

219
00:10:29,590 --> 00:10:31,550
I am sleepy.

220
00:10:34,270 --> 00:10:36,310
If you don't study well,
what could you do then?

221
00:10:37,100 --> 00:10:39,190
Like Dad? Drinking alcohol
and fishing all day?

222
00:10:40,350 --> 00:10:42,150
But I think fishing is meaningful.

223
00:10:42,270 --> 00:10:43,820
However, I don't like studying.

224
00:10:44,070 --> 00:10:45,670
It's enough to have you
in our family studying.

225
00:10:47,630 --> 00:10:49,100
Write down all these quickly!

226
00:10:50,190 --> 00:10:50,710
You are back.

227
00:10:52,710 --> 00:10:54,990
Wang Lao San isn't genuine!

228
00:10:55,110 --> 00:10:57,110
He always bargains over the fishes' price.

229
00:10:57,750 --> 00:10:58,710
But price was set.

230
00:10:59,790 --> 00:11:01,350
We argued the whole day

231
00:11:01,470 --> 00:11:02,630
just for a few cents!

232
00:11:02,790 --> 00:11:03,830
I won't sell them to him next time.

233
00:11:04,110 --> 00:11:05,630
You're bragging! Don't you always say
the same thing?

234
00:11:06,150 --> 00:11:07,310
Dad, you're back!

235
00:11:07,950 --> 00:11:08,670
Son!

236
00:11:11,220 --> 00:11:12,190
Studying?

237
00:11:13,190 --> 00:11:14,350
Study well!

238
00:11:14,670 --> 00:11:15,990
If you get double 100%,

239
00:11:16,190 --> 00:11:17,470
I will buy toys for you.

240
00:11:20,900 --> 00:11:22,910
Xiao Wan, is the allowance
for needy students

241
00:11:22,910 --> 00:11:23,980
ready to be applied?

242
00:11:24,630 --> 00:11:25,430
How did you know that?

243
00:11:25,910 --> 00:11:27,150
Your teacher just posted the news.

244
00:11:27,710 --> 00:11:29,110
It's more than one thousand yuan!

245
00:11:29,350 --> 00:11:32,070
That is 50% more than last year.

246
00:11:32,270 --> 00:11:33,790
Last year, you didn't apply it well

247
00:11:34,230 --> 00:11:34,950
and hid from us.

248
00:11:35,030 --> 00:11:36,910
This year, you must bring the money back!

249
00:11:37,390 --> 00:11:38,030
Understand?

250
00:11:40,750 --> 00:11:42,670
I am recently busy
with the class streaming

251
00:11:42,910 --> 00:11:44,340
and I don't have time for that.

252
00:11:44,670 --> 00:11:47,630
Also, our home is not that poor.

253
00:11:48,190 --> 00:11:49,310
How do the students judge me

254
00:11:49,430 --> 00:11:50,550
if I apply it?

255
00:11:52,550 --> 00:11:54,950
How does this
relate to the class streaming?

256
00:11:56,430 --> 00:11:57,950
We are not that rich.

257
00:11:58,070 --> 00:11:59,030
Do you know that I

258
00:11:59,190 --> 00:12:00,870
spent the whole day argued with others

259
00:12:00,870 --> 00:12:02,590
just for the few cents? Get it?

260
00:12:03,910 --> 00:12:06,310
You just want that dignity, right?

261
00:12:07,220 --> 00:12:09,190
Do I bring disgrace to you
as I am a fisherman?

262
00:12:09,430 --> 00:12:10,470
Enough! Enough!

263
00:12:11,070 --> 00:12:13,060
It's more than one thousand yuan!

264
00:12:13,390 --> 00:12:14,510
Go to sleep now!

265
00:12:15,150 --> 00:12:17,070
Isn't this a great chance?
You tell me!

266
00:12:18,390 --> 00:12:19,110
Xiao Wan.

267
00:12:19,870 --> 00:12:21,390
Your dad doesn't mean anything.

268
00:12:21,990 --> 00:12:23,270
Your results are good and

269
00:12:23,590 --> 00:12:25,110
surely you can get the allowance.

270
00:12:25,790 --> 00:12:27,190
Furthermore, this money

271
00:12:27,350 --> 00:12:29,430
you can keep it as
your college tuition fees.

272
00:12:32,750 --> 00:12:35,110
Sister, let's do homework.

273
00:12:36,950 --> 00:12:37,700
Do it by yourself.

274
00:12:45,670 --> 00:12:46,230
Monitor.

275
00:12:47,030 --> 00:12:47,710
Monitor.

276
00:12:48,310 --> 00:12:49,950
Do we apply for that Community Day
here from you?

277
00:12:50,630 --> 00:12:51,950
Would Wang Yi Ming go too?

278
00:12:52,550 --> 00:12:53,910
Ask the student in charge
